    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused example of this iconic platform, maintained with a 'no-expense-spared' mechanical philosophy. This vehicle features a high-revving naturally aspirated powerplant with optimized volumetric efficiency and a crisp, short-throw manual gearbox. The suspension geometry has been fine-tuned with upgraded bushings and adjustable dampers to minimize body roll and sharpen turn-in response. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul, new high-friction brake pads, and a fresh set of performance-compound tires. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust with excellent compression across all cylinders and a linear power delivery that remains unmatched. Perfect for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience without the 'museum piece' markup.",
